### README

## mTLS client/server

Heartbeat each other with mutual TLS using certificate pinning.

## generate certificates

go run $GOROOT/src/crypto/tls/generate_cert.go -host localhost -ecdsa-curve P256
./mtls-bit -id=2 -addr=localhost:8082 -peerAddr=localhost:8081
./mtls-bit -id=1 -addr=localhost:8081 -peerAddr=localhost:8082